---
title: Mushroom-Stuffed Zucchini Boats with Quinoa and Fresh Tomato Salad
description: Zucchini is the perfect vessel for stuffing—once scooped out, their hearty flesh forms a tiny boat for filling. Finely chopped mushrooms are cooked with butter and shallots for a riff  on mushroom duxelles, a classic French preparation. Folded into a quinoa stuffing, it’s divine!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mushroom-stuffed-zucchini-boats-f5a3b7bc.jpg
